remarks.para:
 Here is an example illustrating a way to back up the value of a String variable
 called mStringToBackUp:
 static String MY_STRING_KEY = "storedstring";

public override void OnBackup(ParcelFileDescriptor oldState, BackupDataOutput data, ParcelFileDescriptor newState)
{
  String mStringToBackup = "stringtobackup";

  ASCIIEncoding ascii = new ASCIIEncoding();
  byte[] stringBytes = ascii.GetBytes(mStringToBackup);
  data.WriteEntityHeader(MY_STRING_KEY,stringBytes.Length);
  data.WriteEntityData(stringBytes, stringBytes.Length);
}
